Package: shinyTooltips
Title: Modern, Customizable Interactive Tooltips for Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight framework for creating modern, customizable, interactive 
    tooltips in Shiny applications. Replaces static HTML title attributes and 
    bulky JavaScript tooltip frameworks with a clean, declarative R API. Supports 
    multiple placements, triggers (hover, click, focus), and smooth animations.
